  "body": "### Description\nWhile writing tests for unrelated changes I noticed that requested blocks from our peers, even though these blocks had been saved in the pendingBlocksManager.\nIn BlockPropagationManager in the method maybeRepeatGetBlock() adding a check whether the pendingBlocksManager has that block available fixed the issue in that case.\nIt should be checked whether we need to add a similar check in other areas of the code where we are requesting blocks.\n",
